
---

**StreamFadePanel**  
**Description:**  
Renders live data in a fading stream panel where older values gently disappear, mimicking signal decay.

```markdown
# StreamFadePanel - Temporal Stream Visualizer

StreamFadePanel provides a unique fading effect for real-time metric charts, emphasizing new values and de-emphasizing old ones.

## Features
- Live fade visualization  
- Adjustable decay rate  
- Built with Matplotlib

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamFadePanel.git
cd StreamFadePanel
python visualize.py
